    <item>
      <title>卢拉推动天然气开采引发巴西政府干预担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/lula-s-push-for-natural-gas-raises-intervention-fears-in-brazil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦力推更多、更廉价的天然气，这一举措引发人们担忧，即巴西正在转向干预主义政策，此举可能阻碍巴西石油公司、Equinor ASA 和壳牌等石油巨头的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/lula-s-push-for-natural-gas-raises-intervention-fears-in-brazil</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 15:50:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>帕劳暂停俄罗斯液化天然气“影子”船队船只的旗帜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/palau-suspends-registration-on-russia-linked-sanctioned-ships</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西太平洋岛国帕劳共和国暂时中止了三艘液化天然气运输船的注册，这些运输船最近因与俄罗斯天然气出口有联系而受到美国制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/palau-suspends-registration-on-russia-linked-sanctioned-ships</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 15:33:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塔利班法律进一步限制妇女权利引发全球抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/taliban-laws-further-curbing-women-s-rights-bring-global-outcry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿富汗塔利班政府出台的新法律引发了全球的谴责，包括禁止妇女在公共场合讲话或露面，并可能危及该政权争取合法性的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/taliban-laws-further-curbing-women-s-rights-bring-global-outcry</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 15:22:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
